channel.title: Project: RealityScape
channel.description:
Hello! I am going to create an uniqe server! A highly respected server, and its not just to type: "::moneyplz" and you have 999m, no,no! You have to earn money, I will try adding quests, and Sound Effects of course. I've even seen servers with music, I will try to add. I will also include:
Lost City quest Monkey Madness quest (short version)
Pest Control and castle wars and much more.
Wish me good luck with my project ;)
